              <description><![CDATA[<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->You are invited to join a unique social media experiment to help us to gather some ideas on the changing nature of learning. There are three broad areas we are interested in:</p>
<ul>
<li style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->the changing nature of&nbsp;<strong>pedagogy</strong></li>
<li style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->the changing nature of&nbsp;<strong>work place learning</strong></li>
